{"tha-ap14:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap14:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap14:0.3":"Ekatthambhikattheraapadana ","tha-ap14:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap14:1.2":"mahapugagano ahu; ","tha-ap14:1.3":"Saranam gata ca te buddham, ","tha-ap14:1.4":"saddahanti tathagatam. ","tha-ap14:2.1":"Sabbe sangamma mantetva, ","tha-ap14:2.2":"malam kubbanti satthuno; ","tha-ap14:2.3":"Ekatthambham alabhanta, ","tha-ap14:2.4":"vicinanti brahavane. ","tha-ap14:3.1":"Teham aranne disvana, ","tha-ap14:3.2":"upagamma ganam tada; ","tha-ap14:3.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap14:3.4":"paripucchim ganam aham. ","tha-ap14:4.1":"Te me puttha viyakamsu, ","tha-ap14:4.2":"silavanto upasaka; ","tha-ap14:4.3":"Malam mayam kattukama, ","tha-ap14:4.4":"ekatthambho na labbhati. ","tha-ap14:5.1":"Ekatthambham mamam detha, ","tha-ap14:5.2":"aham dassami satthuno; ","tha-ap14:5.3":"Aharissamaham thambham, ","tha-ap14:5.4":"appossukka bhavantu te. ","tha-ap14:6.1":"Te me thambham pavecchimsu, ","tha-ap14:6.2":"pasanna tutthamanasa; ","tha-ap14:6.3":"Tato patinivattitva, ","tha-ap14:6.4":"agamamsu sakam gharam. ","tha-ap14:7.1":"Aciram gate pugagane, ","tha-ap14:7.2":"thambham ahasaham tada; ","tha-ap14:7.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap14:7.4":"pathamam ussapesaham. ","tha-ap14:8.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap14:8.2":"Vimanam upapajjaham; ","tha-ap14:8.3":"Ubbiddham bhavanam mayham, ","tha-ap14:8.4":"Sattabhumam samuggatam. ","tha-ap14:9.1":"Vajjamanasu bherisu, ","tha-ap14:9.2":"paricaremaham sada; ","tha-ap14:9.3":"Pancapannasakappamhi, ","tha-ap14:9.4":"raja asim yasodharo. ","tha-ap14:10.1":"Tatthapi bhavanam mayham, ","tha-ap14:10.2":"sattabhumam samuggatam; ","tha-ap14:10.3":"Kutagaravarupetam, ","tha-ap14:10.4":"ekatthambham manoramam. ","tha-ap14:11.1":"Ekavisatikappamhi, ","tha-ap14:11.2":"udeno nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap14:11.3":"Tatrapi bhavanam mayham, ","tha-ap14:11.4":"sattabhumam samuggatam. ","tha-ap14:12.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap14:12.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap14:12.3":"Anubhomi sukham sabbam, ","tha-ap14:12.4":"ekatthambhassidam phalam. ","tha-ap14:13.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap14:13.2":"yam thambhamadadam tada; ","tha-ap14:13.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap14:13.4":"ekatthambhassidam phalam. ","tha-ap14:14.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap14:14.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap14:14.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap14:14.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap14:15.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekatthambhiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap14:16.1":"Ekatthambhikattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}